		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/t13\/1.5\/16\/1f4e3.png\" alt=\"üì£\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>&nbsp;The Map√∫a Malayan Peer Facilitator's Club is on the lookout for new Peer Facilitators!&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><img src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/t13\/1.5\/16\/1f4e3.png\" alt=\"üì£\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.cslocation@X@Application%20poster%201.png\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Application poster 1.png&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;Application poster 1.png&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;Application poster 1.png&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:1002009,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/malayanmindanao.blackboard.com\/sessions\/F0\/F09DE4E8BE803FA5E69B31C84360321A\/da06ce7ffd19460b9b225393f808b175\/Application%20poster%201.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Application poster 1.png&quot;}\">Application poster 1.png<\/a><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">What's a Peer Facilitator?&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/t8d\/1.5\/16\/1f914.png\" alt=\"ü§î\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/td3\/1.5\/16\/2753.png\" alt=\"‚ùì\"><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">A Peer Facilitator is someone who wants to help their fellow students by providing them guidance and emotional support. So, if you're someone who's willing to learn the skills needed to be a listening ear and a shoulder to lean on, join us now!<\/span><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">To&nbsp;apply, fill out the application form in this link:&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/apc01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com\/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.office.com%2Fr%2FxBD74xfWMy%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0t-S8c1OIBLNX_wFChkcVRcBfZk_U8yTiqaf14UMkFlyoRWvzAvrvIMYQ&amp;data=05%7C01%7Crjlsandoval%40mcm.edu.ph%7C97f7445d833c459ad55d08db9710dc30%7C9ddf6758b8c54ce58bbff8c8cc9dd41d%7C0%7C0%7C638269870921009574%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=G%2FG%2Fspyo%2F%2BPfK2m7aSLnvZ6HPRofILwoHbSvO0%2FMQzc%3D&amp;reserved=0\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">https:\/\/forms.office.com\/r\/xBD74xfWMy<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">Deadline of Applications is on:&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>AUGUST 18, 2023.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">See you then!&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/tf3\/1.5\/16\/2764.png\" alt=\"‚ù§Ô∏è\"><\/p>\n<\/div>",
