		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_1cbc32f3-161c-4b04-9c6a-c75044600e6b\"><br><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-18218894_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;WEEK 3 - Exposure Triangle.pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;WEEK 3 - Exposure Triangle.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;WEEK 3 - Exposure Triangle.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:5561542,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/26\/261956EFB75C5BB9821B5149C93A63FC\/0a94ab6193244eff8a75fea9cc557610\/WEEK%203%20-%20Exposure%20Triangle.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;WEEK 3 - Exposure Triangle.pdf&quot;}\">WEEK 3 - Exposure Triangle.pdf<\/a><\/p><br><\/div><div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_40246010-cec0-48b2-998e-3ff31522164a\"><p>Kindly please familiarize yourselves with the basic camera settings using the camera simulator :)!<\/p><p><strong>LINK:<\/strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/camerasim.com\/original-camerasim\/\">Camera Simulator<\/a><\/p><\/div><div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_119b50e1-fa13-4fd9-b56c-a98a04f9bbe3\"><p><strong>VIDEO DISCUSSION:<\/strong><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/youtube.com\/embed\/rw8p-40i7AA\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/youtube.com\/embed\/rw8p-40i7AA&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/youtube.com\/embed\/rw8p-40i7AA&quot;}\">https:\/\/youtube.com\/embed\/rw8p-40i7AA<\/a><\/p><br><\/div>",
