		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Good evening everyone,<\/p><br><p>I hope you're all doing well! To accommodate the approaching summative assessment deadline, our session tomorrow will be&nbsp;<strong>asynchronous<\/strong>. Please utilize this time wisely, and if you have any questions or need assistance with the activity, feel free to reach out to me via Teams or visit me in the faculty room!<\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Additionally, the photography laboratory will be undergoing renovations starting this Wednesday (September 20, 2023) and will be temporarily unavailable for use. For those who intended to use the lab this week, I will keep you informed about when and where you can access the lab's equipment during this time<\/span><\/p><br><p>Thank you all for your understanding, and I can't wait to see all of your work! If you have any other concerns or need clarification, you know how to reach me! üòÑ<\/p>",
