		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_5ad26dd4-6040-4a05-8df6-8d635a0a1fdb\"><p>Hey guys!&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #333333\">üëãüèª<\/span>&nbsp;<\/p><p><span style=\"color: black\">I've gathered a collection of supplementary learning resources here to help you delve deeper into our topic for this week. Feel free to take a moment to explore these materials and further enhance your understanding before diving into this week's activity!<\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>1. Exposure Triangle Simulator<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">If you have some free time on your hands, give this online simulator of the exposure triangle a shot! T<\/span><span style=\"color: #333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">his tool helps you to easily visualize the combination of the three main exposure settings on a final result of a photograph!<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">You can access it through this link here:&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/dima.fi\/exposure\/\"><span style=\"color: #333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong>https:\/\/dima.fi\/exposure\/<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/p><br><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>2. ISO, Shutter Speed and Aperture Explained | Exposure Basics for Beginners<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Edvpu_939l4\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Edvpu_939l4&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;ISO, Shutter Speed and Aperture Explained | Exposure Basics for Beginners&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:588.625,&quot;height&quot;:441.46875}\">ISO, Shutter Speed and Aperture Explained | Exposure Basics for Beginners<\/a><\/p><br><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>3. Photography Tutorial: ISO, Aperture, Shutter Speed<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/6_B8pVoANyY\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/6_B8pVoANyY&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Photography Tutorial: ISO, Aperture, Shutter Speed&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:597.46875,&quot;height&quot;:448.08861345903773}\">Photography Tutorial: ISO, Aperture, Shutter Speed<\/a><\/p><\/div>",
