		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_496da016-2529-42b0-96aa-6cd90f393cc0\"><p>Hello everyone! This week, I'd like you to explore various styles and types of photography to help you discover which one aligns best with your personal style and aesthetic. Since there are numerous options, listing them all here on the module wouldn't be practical. Instead, I've provided some useful links for you to explore. Check them out!<\/p><pre>&nbsp;<\/pre><br><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong>28 types of photography styles by Adobe:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.adobe.com\/creativecloud\/photography\/discover\/types-of-photography.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">28 Types of Photography<\/span><\/a><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong>23 Types of Photography You Should Know in 2023:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/photographylife.com\/types-of-photography\">23 Types of Photography<\/a><\/p><p><strong>59 Types of Photography You Need to Know (With Examples) :&nbsp;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/expertphotography.com\/types-of-photography\/\">59 Types of Photography<\/a><\/p><\/div>",
