		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_7ea1540d-275e-412f-be62-c9066def1646\"><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Hey guys! Below is a video I created that will hopefully assist you with this week's activity. I want to make it clear that this video is purely instructional, and my intention is not to promote any specific beauty standards or cause offense to anyone through this demonstration. Enjoy the tutorial and I hope you learn something new!&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"color: #333333\">üòÑ<\/span><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/WKXZobXIEEY\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/WKXZobXIEEY&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;MMA105L | Crash Course: Photo Retouching&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:798.1817626953125,&quot;height&quot;:633.2261921690456}\">MMA105L | Crash Course: Photo Retouching<\/a><\/p><\/div>",
