		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_59fab0d9-aa6b-45d8-889d-c659f0e9f51b\"><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">For this demonstration, I will guide you through the process of infusing personality and character into your photographs by adding textures and making use of Photoshop's built-in LUTs (Look-Up Tables). These techniques can also assist you in achieving a particular aesthetic for your photos. Please refer to the video below, and I hope you find valuable insights in this tutorial!<\/span><\/p><h6><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/l8F48JO2w7g\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/l8F48JO2w7g&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;MMA105L | Adding Personality To Your Shots (Textures and Color Lookup)&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:798.1817626953125,&quot;height&quot;:598.6190031864596}\">MMA105L | Adding Personality To Your Shots (Textures and Color Lookup)<\/a>&nbsp;<\/h6><p>Here is the image I used in the video, as well as a link to the texture pack I promised you guys:<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/malayancollegesmindanaoo365-my.sharepoint.com\/:u:\/g\/personal\/lpbaker_mcm_edu_ph\/EbFEOjIJOGxJibQ9HmBXqrABbHC1xtRgR0qD8Nh8sF7twg?e=5FfbrH\">Texture Pack<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-19540250_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;TEXTURE DEMO&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;TEXTURE DEMO&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;TEXTURE DEMO.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:1484861,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/7D\/7D8E155943A68FC262AB4D7CC490D8AB\/6c56666c728746f8949f12c9749365b7\/TEXTURE%20DEMO.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;TEXTURE DEMO&quot;}\">TEXTURE DEMO<\/a><\/p><\/div>",
