		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Dear students,<\/p><br><p>Following our recent M2 summative assessment, we've received inquiries from some of you seeking corrections or clarifications regarding your answers. In order to efficiently address these concerns, we kindly request your assistance in the following way:<\/p><br><p>Please complete the linked OneDrive form, which allows you to specify the particular questions or numbers in the exam that you would like us to review. This will aid us in promptly collating and addressing your requests for corrections or clarifications.<\/p><br><p><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.office.com\/r\/xaCMzPNDWY\">M2 Summative Assessment Corrections and Clarifications Request form.<\/a><\/p><br><p>Your cooperation in this process is greatly appreciated, and we are committed to ensuring that your concerns are addressed as effectively as possible. Thank you for your participation.<\/p><br><p>Sincerely,<\/p><br><p>Sir Neal<\/p>",
