		"ITEM_NAME" : "Module 1 Removal Assessment now Available",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Dear Students of Mathematics in the Modern World,<\/p><br><p>I would like to inform you about an opportunity regarding Module 1. If you received an \"IP\" grade for Module 1, you now have the chance to participate in the M1 Removal Assessment.<\/p><br><p>The removal assessment offers flexibility as you can choose to take it at any time before the designated deadline, which is October 20. To access this assessment, please navigate to the Removal Assessment folder located within our Blackboard course.<\/p><br><p>This assessment is designed to be similar in format to our summative assessment and will also be administered online. However, it is worth noting that there will be a reduced number of items compared to the summative assessment.<\/p><br><p>This is a valuable opportunity to improve your understanding of the material and your overall performance in the course. I encourage you to make the most of it.<\/p><br><p>Should you have any questions or require further information, please do not hesitate to reach out. I am here to support your success in Mathematics in the Modern World.<\/p><br><p>Best regards,<\/p><p>Sir Neal<\/p>",
