		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Hello, Class!&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>A quick reminder about accessing materials in our Blackboard course:<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>You may have noticed that for some items, like FA1.1, it's displaying \"Content Isn't Available.\" This is because&nbsp;<strong>our course follows a sequential structure<\/strong>. To access any item, it's important to have gone through the items that come before it. This ensures that you have the foundational knowledge needed to succeed in each step of our learning journey.<\/p>\n <p>In a nutshell:<\/p>\n <br>\n <ul>\n  <li>You need to engage with the previous items before you can access the next ones.<\/li>\n  <li>Sequential progression is key to unlocking content.<\/li>\n <\/ul>\n <br>\n <p>Thank you for your attention to this. Your dedication to following the course structure will contribute greatly to your understanding and success.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Best regards,&nbsp;<\/p>\n <p>Sir Neal Lasta<\/p>\n<\/div>",
