		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_07370403-4030-4b2e-9804-a63518b1443b\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17764524_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;mmpcm.JPG&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;mmpcm.JPG&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;mmpcm.JPG.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:14986,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/24\/24BF1F39BB94E9D0DC7836F4E2F9B2FB\/ade76226db424060b9ae5fa1292b86da\/mmpcm.JPG&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;mmpcm.JPG&quot;}\">mmpcm.JPG<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n <br> \n <br> \n <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Welcome Message<\/h4> \n <br> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17764525_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;tao.jpg&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;tao.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;tao.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:153829,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/D8\/D83070E24C8175BE6D51C1EE7D4A1A5E\/10ee995ee9604f7a940148e7fc7ba591\/tao.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;tao.jpg&quot;}\">tao.jpg<\/a><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">Welcome to Mathematics in the Modern World!<\/span><\/p> \n <p>My name is&nbsp;<strong>Neal Alfie Y. Lasta<\/strong>&nbsp;and I am your new teacher for this course.<\/p> \n <p>You will use Blackboard to:<\/p> \n <ol> \n  <li>Share Course Materials and Documents<\/li> \n  <li>Submit Assignments, take Quizzes<\/li> \n  <li>Communicate with me and each other.<\/li> \n <\/ol> \n <br> \n <p>If you haven't already, you also need to join our Microsoft Teams channel. I sent an invitation link in the Announcements.<\/p> \n <p>We will be using MS Teams as our means of communication and I hope you will make it a habit to check the application for announcements, synchronous session schedules, etc.&nbsp;<\/p> \n <p><em>You can always contact me in MS Teams via Direct Message or through my email<\/em>,&nbsp;<strong>naylasta@mcm.edu.ph<\/strong>, for concerns and questions.<\/p> \n <p>I am pleased to have you as my students and I look forward to working with you for the remaining weeks of this term. I will continue what the previous teacher has started and add a few resources on my own.<\/p> \n <p>To be successful in your studies, you need to be self-motivated to get the work done. Here's a piece of advice I got online: Dedicate 3 or 4 blocks of time every week to work on this course.<\/p> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_b450513d-fa8a-4b09-abfe-f9accf822b1e\"> \n <h5>Contact Information<\/h5> \n <br> \n <p>You can contact me through the following info:<\/p> \n <p>e-mail address:&nbsp;<strong>naylasta@mcm.edu.ph<\/strong><\/p> \n <p>Teams private chat:&nbsp;<strong>Neal Alfie Y. Lasta<\/strong><\/p> \n <p>personal cellphone number:&nbsp;<strong>0936 045 3029&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p> \n <p>I prefer that you message me during the work hours (8:00 AM - 5:00 PM), but if it's an important matter feel free to message me any time of the day, at any day, and I will reach out to you when I have the time.<\/p> \n<\/div>",
