		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_e2a7ece0-d318-4378-ae31-4688ab2f94a7\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>At the end of the lesson, the students will be able to:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">identify the different kinds of diet; and <\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">understand the meaning of each diet.<\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-18018295_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;gif2.gif&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;gif2.gif&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;gif2.gif&quot;,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/58\/58B17416B4B2FC8671A2520712F0BBFA\/1e140b48a35648a7867cd0d4f93deb8b\/gif2.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;gif2.gif&quot;}\">gif2.gif<\/a><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Reference: Google images<\/p> \n <br> \n <br> \n<\/div>",
