		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Hi, students. THIS IS A SPECIAL BIN FOR STUDENTS WHO HAVEN'T TAKEN THEIR 1ST EXAM FOR THIS SUBJECT. Since we have limited time to schedule another special exam whether F2F or online, I have decided to have your special exam as an online submission. This benefits specially to those fully online\/async students.<\/p><br><p><strong>Instructions<\/strong>: (Except for those who are already done!)<\/p><br><p>1. Please see RUBRIC attached below.&nbsp;<\/p><p>2. You must answer the 3 questions below in 90 seconds. No need to mention the questions.<\/p><p>3. Find the questions below.<\/p><p>4. Video-record yourself answering the questions. Take note of the rubric (attached pdf).<\/p><p>5. Respond your link to your video below (Response section).<\/p><br><p><strong>Questions to answer<\/strong>:<\/p><br><ol><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Why is knowing your audience significant in oral communication?<\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Is intercultural understanding a pre-requisite to being an effective communicator?<\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Is context pertinent and important in communication? Explain.<\/span><\/li><\/ol><br><br><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.location@X@INDIVIDUAL%20ORAL%20RUBRIC.pdf\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;INDIVIDUAL ORAL EXAM RUBRIC.pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;INDIVIDUAL ORAL EXAM RUBRIC.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;INDIVIDUAL ORAL RUBRIC.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:113749,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/14\/145CF5A8E5212A1A0B2CA79CFC7E5C24\/fa0b2a4ae1d543ef808618b68e7fa4b0\/INDIVIDUAL%20ORAL%20RUBRIC.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;INDIVIDUAL ORAL EXAM RUBRIC.pdf&quot;}\">INDIVIDUAL ORAL EXAM RUBRIC.pdf<\/a><\/p><br><br><p><span style=\"color: #454545\">DEADLINE:&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\"><strong>5:00 PM, FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 8, 2023<\/strong><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #454545\">Please do it asap.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #454545\">Thank you, good luck.<\/span><\/p>",
