		"ITEM_NAME" : "FINAL SCHEDULE FOR THE MOCK JOB INTERVIEW (OCT. 6 FRIDAY @ 3:45-5:00 PM)",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Dear students,<\/p><br><p>We will have our final schedule for the Mock Job Interview tomorrow on Friday (Oct. 6, 2023) between 3:45-5:00 pm. This schedule is assigned to my other section, C212, in Room 406. If you have time, please come. However, I'll prioritize C212 first. I'll try to have enough time for everyone.<\/p><br><p>Now, Mock Interview is worth 16 points only, and it's part of the Formative Assessment that is 30% of your total grade. In my opinion and this is your choice only, as long as you have a good score during the Final Interview (M2 Final Assessment\/Exam) on October 7, 2023 (Saturday) on 3rd floor - which is 70% of your total grade, I am certain that you will pass your Module 2 even without the Mock Interview, given that you also accomplish all activities we have done so far in the module. However, it's still better to have the Mock Interview for practice and advice.<\/p><br><p>Also, don't forget to submit your Cover Letter and CV on your Blackboard as well.<\/p><br><p>Please please follow the instructions and announcements I have been posting on your Blackboard and Teams.&nbsp;<\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>DON'T FORGET: Final Interview (M2 Final Assessment\/Exam) on October 7, 2023 (Saturday). Please see BB Announcements.<\/strong><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Good luck. Have a nice day!<\/span><\/p><br><br>",
