		"ITEM_ID" : 390878886,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "FINALIZATION OF YOUR GRADES: PLEASE ANSWER ALL \"GRADED\" TASKS IN YOUR MODULE",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Hi, everyone. I'll give you until today to accomplish such \"graded\" tasks. Tomorrow is our deadline for the submission of your grades.&nbsp;<\/p><p>Reporting is 30 points under formative assessment. Fully online students, late enrollees, and others, you can still catch up with graded activities - always check \"Submission Bin for Online Students\/ Daily Log\" in your module. All instructions are already there. Send me message thru Teams if you have any concerns then.<\/p><br><p>For those who have completed the tasks, but still failed or IP. Most likely you may have failed or haven't taken the exam (Individual Oral Presentation). Again, major exams are 70% of your total module grade.<\/p><br><p>For those who haven't taken their exams, please message me thru Teams. Prepare a valid reason as to why.<\/p><br><p>For late enrollees, I understand that you are told to catch up. So, I'll give you a week extension.<\/p><br><br><br><p>Thank you. God bless.<\/p>",
