		"ITEM_NAME" : "NO SYNC CLASS TODAY \/ POSTPONEMENT OF MOCK INTERVIEW - SEPTEMBER 27, 2023",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Good morning, everyone.&nbsp;<\/p><br><p>I would like to inform you that I can't go to class today. I called in sick. I tried my best to get up, but I feel dizzy because of fever. I hope you understand. Let's go asynchronous for today.&nbsp;I'm afraid I&nbsp;&nbsp;have to postpone Dreamybulls and CEA's mock interview - they will be rescheduled to Monday together with Fantastic 4. This means we will have 2 batches only - 3 groups each batch (Please see Announcements again). I'll see you on Monday. I hope this helps you get ample time to prepare. Thank you so much.<\/p><br><p>Thank you so much.<\/p>",
