		"COURSE_NAME" : "Purposive Communication",
		"ITEM_ID" : 387038588,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "PLEASE SEE 1ST EXAM: MODULE 1 FINAL ASSESSMENT SUBMISSION BIN UNDER COURSE CONTENT",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">FOR THOSE WHO HAVEN'T TAKEN THEIR EXAM FOR THIS SUBJECT, THIS IS YOUR LAST CHANCE. PLEASE SEE&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>1ST EXAM: MODULE 1 FINAL ASSESSMENT SUBMISSION BIN<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\">&nbsp;UNDER COURSE CONTENT.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>",
