		"COURSE_NAME" : "Purposive Communication",
		"ITEM_ID" : 390878888,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "RE: STUDENTS WHO GOT IP OR INC",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>For students who got IP, I'm still going to give you time to comply within this month. If you have completed all tasks and joined FTF but still IP, I'm still considering for a removal exam. However, highest grade if you complied IP is still 3.0 (passing grade).<\/p><br><p>For INCs, you can still get higher than 3.0 (passing grade) - but these are students who asked permission from me since they got sick or suffered from a loss.&nbsp;<\/p><br><p>What to do: For now, please wait for Announcements in your Canvas or during FTF sessions.<\/p><br><p>Don't worry. Let's find ways for you as long as you promise to do better next time.<\/p><br><p>For now, it's&nbsp;<strong>Sunday<\/strong>. I am required to take a rest for personal and religious reasons. I may not be able to receive and reply to your messages. Let's stick to working hours.<\/p><br><br><p>I hope you understand. Thank you.<\/p>",
