		"ITEM_NAME" : "UPDATE: M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT\/ EXAM - PUBLIC SPEAKING",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>NOVEMBER 6, 2023 (MONDAY) - PUBLIC SPEAKING (M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT)<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p><em>The schedule is moved to Monday due to the recent announcement of making November 3 as remote learning\/working day.<\/em><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p><strong>WHAT TIME:&nbsp;<\/strong><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>2:30 - 3:45 PM&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\">(<\/span>MUST ARRIVE EARLY)<\/p><p><strong>WHAT TO WEAR:&nbsp;<\/strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\"><strong>FORMAL\/BUSSINESS<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p><strong>WHAT TO BRING:&nbsp;<\/strong><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>2 COPIES OF YOUR PRINTED SPEECH SCRIPT AND RUBRIC<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p><strong>WHERE:&nbsp;<\/strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\"><strong>MMCM PLAZA<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p><strong>NOTE:&nbsp;<\/strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\"><strong>THIS IS THE ONLY SCHEDULE FOR FTF PUBLIC SPEAKING&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\">(M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT).<\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>All online students will be grouped with the FTF groups.<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d\"><strong>&nbsp;Please find your members.<\/strong><\/span><\/p><br><br><p>Good luck!<\/p><br><p><em>Please see Blackboard for M3 Final Assessment - Public Speaking for the rubric and details.<\/em><\/p>",
