		"ITEM_NAME" : "WEEK 12 REHEARSAL & WEEK 13 - M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT - PUBLIC SPEAKING (NOV. 3)",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>OCT. 23 W12D1 F2F &amp; OCT. 25 W12D2 F2F ACTIVITIES<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><br><p>What:<strong>&nbsp;Group Rehearsal &amp; Consultation (for M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT - PUBLIC SPEAKING)<\/strong><\/p><p>What to prepare:<strong>&nbsp;Speech Script&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p><p>When:&nbsp;<strong>October 23 and 25, 2023 (2 days)<\/strong><\/p><p>What time:<strong>&nbsp;2:30 - 3:45 PM<\/strong><\/p><p>Where:<strong>&nbsp;Room 411 (Oct 23), and Room 406 (Oct 25)<\/strong><\/p><br><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>ATTENTION:<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>&nbsp;For full online sync and async students, you should form a group at this time already - either you join a group in the list of FTF group above or you make your own group with other students who don't have groups yet. Please communicate each other through your GC or Team. \"No output submission for these days\".<\/strong><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>If you were not able to join the Public Speaking (M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT - PUBLIC SPEAKING), \"you must do it yourself in front of the public in school\".<\/strong><\/span><\/p><br><p><strong>NO APPEARANCE ON&nbsp;<\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT, NO GRADE.<\/strong><\/span><\/p><br><p><em>Please see Blackboard for M3 Final Assessment - Public Speaking for the rubric and details.<\/em><\/p><br><p>===============================================================================<\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>NOVEMBER 3, 2023 (FRIDAY) - PUBLIC SPEAKING (M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT)<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>WHAT TIME:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>&nbsp;2:30 - 3:45 PM&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">(MUST ARRIVE EARLY)<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>WHAT TO WEAR:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>&nbsp;FORMAL\/BUSSINESS<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>WHAT TO BRING:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>&nbsp;LAPTOP W\/ HDMI FOR PPT PRESENTATION; PRINTED RUBRIC<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>WHERE:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>&nbsp;MMCM PLAZA<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>NOTE:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>&nbsp;THIS IS THE ONLY SCHEDULE FOR FTF PUBLIC SPEAKING&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">(M3 FINAL ASSESSMENT).<\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p>Good luck!<\/p><br><p><em>Please see Blackboard for M3 Final Assessment - Public Speaking for the rubric and details.<\/em><\/p><br><p>===============================================================================<\/p>",
