		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <br>\n <p>Hello, class. How's your weekend so far? I hope you have enjoyed your break.<\/p>\n <p>The modules are already open. For now, you may read the introduction\/overview of the course, and start scanning the lessons.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: left;\">A203 Class Schedule (<span style=\"color: #046ef6\"><strong>ENG041<\/strong><\/span>):<\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>2:30 ‚Äì 3:45 p.m. (Monday) - Blended\/F2F Room 411<\/strong><\/p>\n <p><strong>2:30 ‚Äì 3:45 p.m. (Wednesday) - Blended\/F2F Room 405<\/strong><\/p>\n <p><strong>2:30 ‚Äì 3:45 p.m. (Friday) - Virtual\/Asynchronous<\/strong><\/p>\n <br>\n <p>See you in school on Monday. I'm looking forward to meeting you next week.<\/p>\n<\/div>",
