		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17863234_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_ecc7a495-92f3-46b7-b827-00eee28925c1\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;tumblr_inline_o30jnbr0Mf1sndsvm_540.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;tumblr_inline_o30jnbr0Mf1sndsvm_540.gif&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;}\">tumblr_inline_o30jnbr0Mf1sndsvm_540.gif<\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_c581bb75-9298-449d-b77f-13f800feff53\"> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Course Description<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Purposive Communication is about writing, speaking, and presenting to different audiences and for various purposes. Purposive Communication is a three-unit course that develops students‚Äô communicative competence and enhances their cultural and intercultural awareness through multimodal tasks that provide them opportunities for communicating effectively and appropriately to a multicultural audience in a local or global context. It equips students with tools for critical evaluation of a variety of texts and focuses on the power of language and the impact of images to emphasize the importance of conveying messages responsibly. The knowledge, skills, and insights that students gain from this course may be used in their academic endeavors, their chosen disciplines, and their future careers as they compose and produce relevant oral, written, audio-visual and\/or web-based output for various purposes.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n<\/div> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17863237_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_71723476-76c1-41bf-b55d-2945d092001f\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Course Outcomes.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Course Outcomes.jpg&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;}\">Course Outcomes.jpg<\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_dabd9b7d-1e9a-4efd-8ead-53fa2e221437\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>Course References<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Textbook<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> <\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Madrunio, M. &amp; Martin, I. (2018). Purposive communication: Using English in Multilingual Contexts. Quezon: C&amp;E Publishing, Inc.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>References<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Anderson (2018). Technical Communication. Cengage Coopman, S. &amp; Lull, J. (2014). Public speaking: The evolving art (4th Edition). USA: Cengage Learning. Henson, R. (2018). Purposive communication. Quezon: C&amp;E Publishing, Inc. <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Keith, W.M. (2018). Public speaking: Choices and Responsibility. Australia: Cengage Learning. Kolin. (2015).Successful Writing at Work: Concise Edition. Cengage Uychoco, M.T.A. (2018). Communication for Society: Purposive Communication. Manila: Rex Book Store, Incorporated.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div>",
