		"ITEM_NAME" : "ultraDocumentBody",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_c27eb407-6776-476a-bbc8-9311d73dd22d\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">This course aims to assist and equip students to gain proper knowledge and skills on building their career path. To discover their potential\/s that would correspond to their future profession; develop their potential into skills; able to demonstrate basic and appropriate work behavior; and be deployed towards internships and employment.&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Producing the ideal Map√∫a Graduate with triple-threat traits - encompassing the four strands of MMCM‚Äôs employability framework: (1) career awareness and development, (2) employability attributes, (3) cooperative education, and (4) global opportunities.<\/span><\/span><\/p><\/div>",
