		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Hello, class!&nbsp;<\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Please tell us a little bit about yourself, your program and why you chose it, your location, and other things you might want to share with the class. You may interact with your classmates by commenting on their replies.<\/span><\/p><br>",
