		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Dear MMCM students,<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>As we are finalizing the onboarding process for our esteemed faculty members, you may explore the uploaded learning materials.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Rest assured, we are working diligently to ensure a smooth transition and an exceptional academic experience for all.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Stay tuned for further updates and details.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Thank you,<\/p>\n <br>\n<\/div>",
