		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_eb140611-ef33-4b96-bd2f-e8e07e8f1fa4\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Introduction<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">The term literature cannot be separated with literary appreciation. Literary appreciation is the ability to understand, enjoy, and evaluate literary works. It studies the writing styles and literary devices which are used within texts. Literature is the object that literary appreciation looks to study and the medium through which literary appreciation can be expressed.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17840204_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_e34996ae-ccbc-4bb5-a0fd-ec8694728a2b\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;IdleCostlyBaiji-size_restricted.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;IdleCostlyBaiji-size_restricted.gif&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;}\">IdleCostlyBaiji-size_restricted.gif<\/a> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_891e4259-6f2d-432b-93f2-1ad96bce5af0\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210730233642.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17840206_1\"><\/a> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_927abd81-0b52-4d44-b133-7e7d1d5f1966\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210730234549.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17840212_1\"><\/a> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17840213_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_a08ee9cc-8a82-4a54-8339-c4009a6c9229\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _17_.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _17_.png&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;}\">Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _17_.png<\/a> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17840214_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_79949a9b-23a2-4ae7-af67-dce8861ef0a6\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _18_.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _18_.png&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;}\">Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _18_.png<\/a>",
