		"ITEM_NAME" : "ECE121L-A261 F2F EXAM ANNOUNCEMENT",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p><strong>We will have the F2F Summative Assessment for ECE121L-A261 this Saturday (09\/23\/2023) at R602 from 7:00AM to 10:45AM.<\/strong><\/p><br><p>The Summative Assessment coverage includes the following:<\/p><ol><li>Equations and variables in MATLAB,<\/li><li>MATLAB Arrays and Matrices - matrix operations, matrix manipulations and special matrices,<\/li><li>MATLAB Mathematical Operations - polynomial multiplication, division, roots, symbolic differential, partial differentiation, and integration.<\/li><\/ol><br><p>Please be reminded that the Summative Assessment is strictly F2F. Absence without valid reason and valid proof will automatically have a minimum score in the exam. You can use your own laptop during the exam so that you can access your references more conveniently.<\/p>",
