		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <h4><span style=\"color: #1c8845\">Good day A244!<\/span>&nbsp;<\/h4>\n <br>\n <p>Welcome to&nbsp;<strong>ENGINEERING ECONOMY (EECO102)<\/strong>. This is a reminder for this week's schedule.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>08 - 08 - 2023 Tuesday<\/strong><\/span>: Course Orientation (Engr. Binghay)&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>08 - 10 - 2023 Thursday<\/strong><\/span>: Pre - Assessment (An overview of the topics of the course) This will be available in the blackboard.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><strong>08 - 12 - 2023 Saturday<\/strong><\/span>: F2F Class (Topic: Introduction to Engineering Economy Principles and Terminologies in Engineering Economy)<\/p>\n<\/div>",
