		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_ffb49247-6f42-4c1d-bb0b-f5525e9e870d\"> \n <p>Hi Students,<\/p> \n <p><span style=\"color: #5f6368\"><strong>Geologists<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #4d5156\">&nbsp;are critical thinkers who look at a wide array of different sorts of data to figure out how the Earth works.&nbsp;<\/span>Critical thinking begins with reasoning and the application of the Scientific method in solving a problem entails the usage of reasoning. Please listen to the lecture embedded below.<\/p> \n <p><a href=\"https:\/\/mcm.ap.panopto.com\/Panopto\/Pages\/Viewer.aspx?id=4e96adc2-4670-4e1f-b061-ad8801764726&amp;start=0\">Critical Thinking: Scientific Method and Theory<\/a><\/p> \n <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=-nAYmCimxhA\">The Origin of the Scientific Method | Origins: The Journey of Humankind<\/a><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_070e541c-2845-47ec-9e60-58a00be8184c\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210818231245.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-18186999_1\"><\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_bf7ff1ef-83a8-46af-a14d-0eeb81ae11b0\"> \n <p>Deductive Reasoning<\/p> \n <ul> \n  <li>It is unsafe to play in the rain. It is raining today. So, it would be dangerous to play now<\/li> \n  <li>All fruits have vitamins. All apples are fruits. Therefore, all apples have vitamins<\/li> \n  <li>All amphibians are cold-blooded. All frogs are amphibians. Therefore, all frogs are cold-blooded<\/li> \n  <li>All Pets are loyal. All dogs are pets. Therefore, all dogs are loyal<\/li> \n  <li>All human beings are mortal. James is a human being. Thus, James is mortal<\/li> \n <\/ul> \n <br> \n <p>Inductive Reasoning<\/p> \n <ul> \n  <li>Socrates is a grandfather. Socrates is bald. Therefore, all grandfathers are bald<\/li> \n  <li>Jim is a baby. Jim is gentle. Therefore, all babies are gentle<\/li> \n  <li>Texas is a city. Texas is clean. Therefore, all towns are clean<\/li> \n  <li>Pigeons, doves, and eagles are birds. They can all fly. Therefore, all birds can fly<\/li> \n  <li>Joy, Cate, and Brad are teachers. They are all nice. Therefore, all the teachers are nice<\/li> \n <\/ul> \n <br> \n<\/div>",
