		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_e85ab4b0-4010-4fab-9bed-8b3136d4e0dd\"> \n <p>Hi Students! Good day. Let's start deciphering the history\/past of Earth's dynamism and evolution over time thru this lecture about Continental Drift Theory by Wegner.<\/p> \n <p>Please watch and listen to the embedded video below or you can click the link provided below.<\/p> \n <p><a href=\"https:\/\/mcm.ap.panopto.com\/Panopto\/Pages\/Viewer.aspx?id=35fdcab6-ba32-456b-9d4c-ad84010b7983&amp;start=0\">Lecture 2 - Understanding the Earth - Continental Drift Theory<\/a> .<\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_39d1e87c-f543-4a56-a804-c40e8a3ed83c\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210814164357.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-18067862_1\"><\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_45157133-dce5-4277-b831-39f0325594ef\"> \n <p><span style=\"color: #046ef6\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Hi Students, to provide you a concise and full elaboration of Continental Drift Theory, please watch and listen to embedded pertinent video below.<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_81352eed-4916-4d72-8d01-1ff510fb0927\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210814170117.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-18067866_1\"><\/a>",
