		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_61a8fe5e-1859-4fe6-a256-f076a233d51b\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Hello Class! Since this is the start of your fitness journey this term, it would be a good idea to start your undertaking by watching the video below explaining what happens inside our body when we start to workout. Hope that it will motivate and get you excited to see some improvements on your holistic well being at the end of this term.<\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/wWGulLAa0O0\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Initial Activity&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/wWGulLAa0O0&quot;}\">Initial Activity<\/a><\/p> \n<\/div>",
