		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Dear students,<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>A pleasant day to you. For easier communication, please join our group chat via MS Teams. To join, please click this link:<\/p>\n <br>\n <p><a href=\"https:\/\/teams.microsoft.com\/l\/team\/19%3a7BDon-56uKgHpdhSWdE-Tu8B3-d4TjAcPyN7PwjEYzo1%40thread.tacv2\/conversations?groupId=a0bbd42a-e0dc-482b-ac28-2a94b9c4fc2a&amp;tenantId=9ddf6758-b8c5-4ce5-8bbf-f8c8cc9dd41d\">https:\/\/teams.microsoft.com\/l\/team\/19%3a7BDon-56uKgHpdhSWdE-Tu8B3-d4TjAcPyN7PwjEYzo1%40thread.tacv2\/conversations?groupId=a0bbd42a-e0dc-482b-ac28-2a94b9c4fc2a&amp;tenantId=9ddf6758-b8c5-4ce5-8bbf-f8c8cc9dd41d<\/a><\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Sincerely,&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Ma'am Ems<\/p>\n<\/div>",
