		"ITEM_ID" : 430710359,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "Group Speech Practice",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dear students,<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I hope you are having a lovely day. Unfortunately, I cannot present to you a new topic today as much as I want to since my voice is really hoarse from coughing. With that, please use the time later to practice for your speech performance. I will be discussing the lesson on Tuesday instead.<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you have any concerns, please message me via MS Teams.<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thank you very much for understanding.<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sincerely,<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ma'am Ems<\/p>",
