		"ITEM_NAME" : "Group Speech Script Submission ",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Dear students,<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">How are you guys doing?&nbsp;<strong>Please be reminded that the submission of your group speech script is today.<\/strong>&nbsp;You may opt not to attend the class face-to-face today provided that you have submitted your speech online. You may submit it to me via MS Teams. Also, appoint your group leader so that only the group leader will submit the script to me.<\/p><br><p>If you have any questions, please let me know. Thank you!<\/p><br><p>Sincerely,<\/p><br><p>Ma'am Ems<\/p>",
