		"ITEM_NAME" : "Suicide Prevention Awareness",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Hello, Mapuans!<\/p><br><p>As we celebrate the Suicide Prevention Week, let us keep in mind these useful information to help each other create a healthier mental health environment. If you feel the need to talk to someone or you know a friend who needs to be heard, please do not hesitate to reach out to the CGC.&nbsp;<\/p><br><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.cslocation@X@MicrosoftTeams-image.png\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;MicrosoftTeams-image.png&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;MicrosoftTeams-image.png&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;MicrosoftTeams-image.png&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:552338,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/malayanmindanao.blackboard.com\/sessions\/FB\/FBD44B2FAE08734F3A7A90D8F45BB2E9\/49fc6bfc495e406e91361fad9691c794\/MicrosoftTeams-image.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;MicrosoftTeams-image.png&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:739.1875,&quot;height&quot;:1846.1548091805344}\">MicrosoftTeams-image.png<\/a><\/p><br><br><p>You may send us a message thru this FB Page, send us an email at guidance@mcm.edu.ph, or visit us onsite in our temporary OSS Office near the Playcourt.<\/p><br><p>Thank you!<\/p><br><p>Sincerely, &nbsp;<\/p><br><p>&nbsp;The Center for Guidance and Counseling &nbsp;<\/p><p>+63 998 595 0023 \/ guidance@mcm.edu.ph &nbsp;<\/p><br><p>We care for your wellness ‚ù£<\/p>",
