		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Hey class!<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>I will be your course lecture professor for&nbsp;<strong>Digital Photography<\/strong>&nbsp;this first term! I am currently reconstructing the course syllabus and modules to give you guys a better benefiting experience. I am hoping to upload the&nbsp;<em>Module 1<\/em>&nbsp;materials before the end of this week, so please check your&nbsp;<strong>Blackboard<\/strong>&nbsp;from time to time.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Most of our lecture classes will be online<\/span>.&nbsp;<strong>Lecture classes<\/strong>&nbsp;are different from your&nbsp;<strong>laboratory classes<\/strong>&nbsp;so please check your class schedules diligently.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>We did not meet last week and so I am hoping to meet all of you this week. And since our lecture class this month will be online, I&nbsp;<strong>HIGHLY<\/strong>&nbsp;suggest you&nbsp;<strong>attend our meetings<\/strong>&nbsp;especially for this week.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>See you at&nbsp;<strong>9:30 am, tomorrow<\/strong>! (I know it's too early)<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Should you have any&nbsp;<em>concerns<\/em>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<em>inquiries<\/em>, please don‚Äôt hesitate to message me through&nbsp;<strong>Microsoft Teams<\/strong>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>All the best,<\/p>\n <p>Ms. Patly<\/p>\n <br>\n<\/div>",
