		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Good evening class!<\/p><br><p>I hope you're all doing well. I'd just like to clarify that our class tomorrow, and every proceeding session, will be held at the backstage of the auditorium while the photo lab is undergoing renovations.&nbsp;<\/p><br><p>See you all tomorrow!&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #333333\">üòÑ<\/span><\/p>",
