		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Good afternoon students!<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>I am thrilled to announce that I will be your course instructor for your&nbsp;<strong>Digital Photography Laboratory<\/strong>&nbsp;this semester! Over the weekend, I will be finalizing and organizing our course modules here on Blackboard, so please keep an eye out for that as this space will serve as our centralized hub for accessing digital resources, assessments, and discussions.<\/p>\n \n <p>Now given the current circumstances, we do have a bit of ground to cover, so I am anticipating your presence in our first&nbsp;<strong>face-to-face session<\/strong>&nbsp;next week where we will finally be able to jumpstart this semester together!<\/p>\n \n <p>In the meantime, if you have any questions, thoughts, or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact me via Teams or Outlook.<\/p>\n \n <p>Looking forward to meeting you guys real soon!&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000\">üòÅ<\/span><\/p>\n \n <p>Best Regards,<\/p>\n <p>Liam Patrick A. Baker<\/p>\n<\/div>",
