		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Good afternoon guys!&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #333333\">üëãüèª<\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">First of all, congratulations to each one of you for completing the first module of your Digital Photography Laboratory! I hope you've all gained valuable insights and skills along the way. As we move forward into the second module, please be aware that all submission bins for our previous formative assessments have now been closed.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">For your summative assessment, the submission bin will close&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>tonight at 6:00 PM<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\">, and this will be the final extension I will give for this assessment (with consequent deductions). If you encounter any issues or have concerns regarding your submission, please don't hesitate to reach out to me via Teams, and we will evaluate whether your situation warrants any special considerations.<\/span><\/p><br><p>We'll be starting our second and final module for this term next week, so I hope you'll all be present during our session! Thank you guys, and enjoy your weekend!&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #333333\">üòÑ<\/span><\/p>",
