		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Good evening guys!<\/p><br><p>I hope you're all having a great week so far. I'd just like to announce that we will still be having our&nbsp;<strong>first session tomorrow at 1:15 PM<\/strong>, as you are all still required to attend your classes regardless of the college acquaintance party. For those of you with DSLR cameras at home, I highly encourage you to bring them tomorrow!<\/p><br><p>Furthermore, in light of the ongoing events tomorrow, our&nbsp;<em>tentative<\/em>&nbsp;classroom for this session will also be moved to&nbsp;<strong>R516 in the Academic Building<\/strong>&nbsp;instead of the photography laboratory. This is so our class will not be disrupted by the festivities going on in the auditorium.<\/p><br><p>I hope these instructions are clear! Enjoy the rest of your night guys, and see you all tomorrow!<\/p>",
