		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Good morning guys!<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>It's just been announced to us that&nbsp;<strong>all classes 10:00 AM onwards will now be asynchronous<\/strong>&nbsp;to make way for the college acquaintance party. So, this means that our face-to-face session later this afternoon will be postponed.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Please refer to the Week 3 folder I posted here on BBL for our topic this week, and you may now also access the instructions and submission bin for our activity this week. If you'd like to have anything clarified or further discussed, feel free to reach out to me via Teams!<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>My apologies for the confusion guys! I was caught off guard by the announcement as well.&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000\">üòÖ<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Have a great day and enjoy the party later this evening!<\/p>\n<\/div>",
