		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Good afternoon guys!&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000\">üëãüèª<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p>I hope you're all having a great week so far! As I mentioned previously during our class, this week we will be tackling both lighting and portrait photography! So, in order for us to be prepared for tomorrow's session, here are a few guidelines I'd like for you to take note of:<\/p>\n <br>\n <ul>\n  <li><span style=\"color: #000000\">For this week's activity, you'll be working in groups. You need at least 2 members, and can have only up to 4. Please choose one member to be your subject or model for the activity.<\/span><\/li>\n <\/ul>\n <br>\n <ul>\n  <li>Our class will be held in the Photography Laboratory (4th Floor Admin Building).<\/li>\n <\/ul>\n <br>\n <ul>\n  <li>If you wish to borrow the DSLR cameras of the Lab, you may do so but please provide your own SD card.<\/li>\n <\/ul>\n <br>\n <ul>\n  <li>You're free to bring any additional backdrops or lighting sources that you'd like to use for our activity.<\/li>\n <\/ul>\n <br>\n <ul>\n  <li>Feel free to get dressed or dolled up for this activity!<\/li>\n <\/ul>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you live within the city, I highly encourage you to attend our face-to-face session. It will make the activity much easier for you!&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Also, just as a heads up, to those who will be absent tomorrow, you will only be able to form groups with other absentees. I will not permit you to join any groups that were formed during the session. You may, however, opt to perform the task individually.<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">I hope these instructions are clear, and I'll see you all tomorrow!&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\">üòÑ<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><em>P.S. Quick reminder that the deadline for your 2nd activity is tonight at 11:59 PM!&nbsp;<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>",
