		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>Good morning everyone,<\/p><br><p>I hope you're all doing well! I‚Äôd like to remind you all once again that our session today will be&nbsp;<strong>asynchronous.&nbsp;<\/strong>This is<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong>so that you guys will be able to use this time to finalize and work on your digital photo books. Please utilize this time wisely, and if you have any questions or need assistance with the activity, feel free to reach out to me via Teams or visit me in the faculty room!<\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Additionally, the photography laboratory is currently undergoing renovations and is temporarily unavailable for use. For those who intended to use the lab this week, I will keep you informed about when and where you can access the lab's equipment during this time.<\/span><\/p><br><p>Thank you all for your understanding, and I can't wait to see all of your work! If you have any other concerns or need clarification, you know how to reach me! üòÑ<\/p>",
