		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_86218437-cb19-447f-a5d0-20efd629a58d\"><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Hey guys! In this demonstration, I will guide you through the process of adding dimension to your photographs through post-processing in Adobe Photoshop. Specifically, we will concentrate on enhancing the depth of field of our images! Kindly refer to the video provided below, and I hope you guys learn something new!<\/span><\/p><h6><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/TDZdPCG_zi0\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/TDZdPCG_zi0&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;MMA105L | Adding Dimension To Your Shot&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:798.1817626953125,&quot;height&quot;:721.8947182592788}\">MMA105L | Adding Dimension To Your Shot<\/a>&nbsp;<\/h6><p>If you'd like to follow along with this demonstration, here is the image I used in the video:<\/p><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-19541942_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;DIMENSION DEMO&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;DIMENSION DEMO&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;DIMENSION DEMO.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:2024529,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/7D\/7D8E155943A68FC262AB4D7CC490D8AB\/2552a43ae80441f3bccdb605d61e37a1\/DIMENSION%20DEMO.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;DIMENSION DEMO&quot;}\">DIMENSION DEMO<\/a><\/p><\/div>",
