		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_3381727f-43ea-4a1b-9825-a6b1f4029b96\"><p>In this demonstration, we will learn how to improve the lighting of our images. We will be tackling two separate methods for achieving this, so kindly refer to the video below and I hope you guys learn something new!<\/p><h6><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/JoLL16uIeEM\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/JoLL16uIeEM&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;MMA105L | Lighting Enhancements&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:798.1817626953125,&quot;height&quot;:633.2261921690456}\">MMA105L | Lighting Enhancements<\/a>&nbsp;<\/h6><p>If you'd like to follow along with this demonstration, here are the images I used in the video:<\/p><h6><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-19541947_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 01&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 01&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 01.png&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:7581641,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/7D\/7D8E155943A68FC262AB4D7CC490D8AB\/6c78c26b76f44497bfb883af8f43ceca\/LIGHTING%20DEMO%2001.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 01&quot;}\">LIGHTING DEMO 01<\/a>&nbsp;<\/h6><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-19541950_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 02&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 02&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 02.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:3004016,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/7D\/7D8E155943A68FC262AB4D7CC490D8AB\/90ed5c4a49db49f896f6c7fd78c26bb9\/LIGHTING%20DEMO%2002.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;LIGHTING DEMO 02&quot;}\">LIGHTING DEMO 02<\/a><\/p><\/div>",
