		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Dear Students,<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Hear are the following details for our upcoming M1 Summative Assessment:<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #a234b5\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">What:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;M1 Summative Assessment<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #046ef6\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">When:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;September 9 - 10, 2023 (Only Available from Saturday to Sunday)<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #1c8845\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Nature:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;Fully-online asynchronous exam with time limit of 1 hour and 30 minutes (1 attempt only)<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Coverage:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;All topics in M1 except for the logic part of \"Sets and Logic\"<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #666666\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Items:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;60 items<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Note that topics that were not discussed directly in the synchronous sessions will still be part of the coverage since it is expected for you to access and study the content even when we are not meeting synchronously.<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Also, we will still have a synchronous&nbsp;<\/span>class<span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;this week to discuss Sets and Venn Diagrams.<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">If you have any questions, please&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">contact me via our Official MS Teams Group<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Cheers,<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Sir Earvin<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>",
