		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Dear Students,<\/p>\n \n <p>I&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">won't be able to meet you synchronously this incoming Thursday<\/span><\/strong>&nbsp;because I have an important family errand to run.<\/p>\n \n <p>However, rest assured that I will be attaching the link to the synchronous sessions conducted from other sections for you to view.<\/p>\n \n <p>As an asynchronous activity, please do your formative assessments in that time so that there won't be any problems in module 1 grade calculation by next week.<\/p>\n \n <p>Thanks have a great day ahead!<\/p>\n \n <p>Cheers,<\/p>\n <p>Sir Earvin<\/p>\n<\/div>",
