		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Dear Students,<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">We still won't be having a class tomorrow since I'm still finalizing the courses in Canvas and Blackboard.<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">However, here is the following schedule for our course orientation and first synchronous class for this week:<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n \n <p><span style=\"color: #E72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Thursday, August 10, 2023, 8:15 - 9:30 AM - Course Orientation and First Synch Session<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Note that since Mathematics in the Modern World is a&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Bichronous Online (BO)<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;course, this means that we&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">will be meeting synchronously once a week and the rest is asynchronous online<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;content.<\/span><\/p>\n \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Again, to emphasize, we will just be meeting in a virtual classroom only once a week.<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The schedule for our synchronous meetings will be every Thursday at the same time slot as the course orientation this week.<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Also, I already set-up an Official MS Teams Group for this section for MATH035 so we will have our synchronous sessions there.<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Lastly, if you have any questions and concerns, please contact me&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">directly using the official MS Teams Group for this section<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Thanks and see you this Thursday and the rest of the Thursdays to come.<\/span><\/p>\n \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Cheers,<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Sir Earvin<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>",
