		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_f199f54f-1894-4bd1-8ef6-8d5d70a7464d\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Module 2 Summative Assessment<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>For those who have completed the month-long fitness program (Weeks 1-4)<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>GUIDELINES:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>PART 1<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">:&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-During the Wellness Day, take a&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #17375e\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">picture<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;of yourself before and after the event wearing the outfit for your presentation. The venue must be at the playcourt with your classmates or professor as the background.&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>PART 2<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">: Write a short&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #17375e\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">essay<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;about your experience in a month-long fitness program.<\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Discuss the following:<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-Challenges, Improvements, Benefits, Realizations, and Experience\/s on the Wellness Day<\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-Give your overall impression of the PE course.&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Submit your output in a&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: red\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">single attachment with multiple pages in a PDF file.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Avoid attaching<\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: red\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;one drive\/Google Drive link<\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">for it will not be checked due to lag issues<\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Grades will be based on the given criteria during the wellness da<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">y.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #002060\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>FAILURE TO FOLLOW THE GIVEN GUIDELINES WOULD MEAN A RESUBMISSION OF OUTPUT AND CERTAIN POINTS WILL BE DEDUCTED<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: red\"><span style=\"font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><br><br><br><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/p><\/div>",
