		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>THIS BIN WILL BE AVAILABLE UNTIL AUGUST 19, 2023<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><ol><li style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\n          padding-left: 1.319rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Create a 30-second PSA explaining and\/or promoting the ''Power of Communication\"<\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\n          padding-left: 1.319rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Video record yourself and submit the link of your output here.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\n          padding-left: 1.319rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Label your output with Family Name_PSA_W2D1<\/span><\/span><\/li><\/ol><br><p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.location@X@W1.D1.jpg\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;W1.D1.jpg&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;W1.D1.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;W1.D1.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:93258,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/AA\/AAFFDA69F5372ED5125099A3EE43A53E\/27a09c8ef54d4caca749c111a22b5e46\/W1.D1.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;W1.D1.jpg&quot;}\">W1.D1.jpg<\/a><\/p>",
