		"ITEM_NAME" : "W2D2: VIDEO ESSAY",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p><span style=\"color: #e72218\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>NOTE: THIS BIN WILL BE AVAILABLE UNTIL AUGUST 19, 2023<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Instructions<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">:<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><ol><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\n          padding-left: 1.487rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Choose one communication model and explain the model using your own words and understanding.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\n          padding-left: 1.487rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Use your own examples to explain the model.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\n          padding-left: 1.487rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">In your example\/s, illustrate the model by showing both successful communication and failed communication.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\n          padding-left: 1.487rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Time: minimum of one minute, maximum of two minutes.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\n          padding-left: 1.487rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Submit the link of your video here.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\n          padding-left: 1.487rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Rename the file with Family name_M2D2_VideoEssay<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><\/ol><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Criteria:<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Structure and Organization (5 points)<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">: Is the video essay logically structured with a clear introduction, body, and conclusion? Are ideas presented in a coherent and organized manner?<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Clarity of Narration (5 points)<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">: Is the narration clear, well-paced, and articulate? Are transitions between different sections smooth and seamless?<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><br><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Audio Quality (5 points)<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">: Is the audio quality clear and free from distracting background noise or distortions? Is the volume level appropriate and consistent?<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>",
