		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Hello everyone!<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">I hope you are all doing fine.<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Please see the table below for the breakdown of our class schedule:<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <table>\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Monday<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/td>\n    <td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Wednesday<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/td>\n    <td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Friday<\/strong><\/span><\/p><\/td>\n   <\/tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">12:00 - 1:15 PM [Room 514]&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><\/td>\n    <td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">12:00 - 1:15 PM [Room 502]&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><\/td>\n    <td><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">12:00 - 1:15 PM [V502]&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><\/td>\n   <\/tr>\n  <\/tbody>\n <\/table>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Note that the \"V\" stands for Virtual, meaning the assigned day with V room will be our asynchronous day.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">In addition, I will make module 1 available tomorrow morning.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">I hope to see you all tomorrow for our first class with the topic \"Course Orientation\".<\/span><\/p>\n <br>\n <br>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Warm regards,<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ms. Jovaira Mangubat<\/span><\/p>\n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\">ENG041 Instructor<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>",
