		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_eb140611-ef33-4b96-bd2f-e8e07e8f1fa4\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Introduction<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Communication is not limited to exchanges between people. It also refers to activities that do not involve people. Being able to communicate effectively is perhaps the most important of all life skills. It is what enables us to pass information to other people, and to understand what is said to us.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Purposive communication is defined as the use of language for different audiences and for different reasons. This course is intended to improve students‚Äô skills in the field of communication. By purposive communication, students can raise awareness of the cultural and intercultural aspects and develop them so that they can interact effectively and accurately with a broad range of audiences, both local and global. Language is used formally and academically in prior knowledge.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">In the context of today‚Äôs age, purposive communication plays an important part in student‚Äôs academic success and future career prospects. In today‚Äôs challenging environment, students must not only possess academic expertise, but also the requisite skills to enhance their learning and employability prospects in the future.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17853353_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_fd619428-6aca-44c1-9f8f-bec6424690f3\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;encounter.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;encounter.gif&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;}\">encounter.gif<\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_a9ed94f0-44fe-45d8-a6ef-0866321925a0\"> \n <p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Course Description<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Purposive Communication is about writing, speaking, and presenting to different audiences and for various purposes. Purposive Communication is a three-unit course that develops students‚Äô communicative competence and enhances their cultural and intercultural awareness through multimodal tasks that provide them opportunities for communicating effectively and appropriately to a multicultural audience in a local or global context. It equips students with tools for critical evaluation of a variety of texts and focuses on the power of language and the impact of images to emphasize the importance of conveying messages responsibly. The knowledge, skills, and insights that students gain from this course may be used in their academic endeavors, their chosen disciplines, and their future careers as they compose and produce relevant oral, written, audio-visual and\/or web-based output for various purposes.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_891e4259-6f2d-432b-93f2-1ad96bce5af0\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210730233642.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17853357_1\"><\/a> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_927abd81-0b52-4d44-b133-7e7d1d5f1966\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210730234549.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17853359_1\"><\/a> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17853360_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_a08ee9cc-8a82-4a54-8339-c4009a6c9229\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _17_.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _17_.png&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;}\">Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _17_.png<\/a> \n<a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17853361_1\" data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_79949a9b-23a2-4ae7-af67-dce8861ef0a6\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _18_.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _18_.png&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;}\">Ivory and Ash Grey Photo DIY Influencer Minimalist Facebook Cover _18_.png<\/a>",
