		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_936db403-2609-4fa2-85f4-0ec83851fe74\"> \n <br> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837740_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;image_processing20200728-3248-1nxe45r.gif&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;image_processing20200728-3248-1nxe45r.gif&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;image_processing20200728-3248-1nxe45r.gif&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:9009280,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/AA\/AAF9C5BAAF72DE1D708EF9CC0F05418D\/706511a602064f7298b3e2c83d26bed1\/image_processing20200728-3248-1nxe45r.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;image_processing20200728-3248-1nxe45r.gif&quot;}\">image_processing20200728-3248-1nxe45r.gif<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_676b28a0-ca96-46c2-95e3-fbc23a7ac4f4\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Overview<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Gilgamesh&nbsp;is the semi-mythic King of&nbsp;Uruk&nbsp;in&nbsp;Mesopotamia&nbsp;best known from&nbsp;The Epic of Gilgamesh&nbsp;(written c. 2150 - 1400 BCE) the great&nbsp;Sumerian\/Babylonian poetic work which pre-dates&nbsp;Homer's writing&nbsp;by 1500 years and, therefore, stands as the oldest piece of epic world&nbsp;literature.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The motif of the quest for the meaning of life is first fully explored in Gilgamesh as the hero-king leaves his kingdom following the&nbsp;death&nbsp;of his best friend, Enkidu, to find the mystical figure Utnapishtim and gain eternal life. Gilgamesh's fear of death is actually a fear of meaninglessness and, although he fails to win immortality, the quest itself gives his life meaning. This theme has been explored by writers and philosophers from antiquity up to the present day.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_493c8397-7be0-4b38-8104-3948b5b0c29b\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson Proper<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_d7364758-8069-47c7-b4be-b7b4c2240dee\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20220730122325.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837742_1\"><\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_a3701d14-ffa1-4e0f-964e-04f8b969f5bf\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Reading Materials<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837749_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;The Epic of Gilgamesh (Full Text).pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;The Epic of Gilgamesh (Full Text).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;The Epic of Gilgamesh (Full Text).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:282550,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/AA\/AAF9C5BAAF72DE1D708EF9CC0F05418D\/37c84e585742438a81c0d2ef019f96a9\/The%20Epic%20of%20Gilgamesh%20%28Full%20Text%29.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;The Epic of Gilgamesh (Full Text).pdf&quot;}\">The Epic of Gilgamesh (Full Text).pdf<\/a><\/p> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837750_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;EPIC OF GILGAMESH (summary).pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;EPIC OF GILGAMESH (summary).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;EPIC OF GILGAMESH (summary).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:230698,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/AA\/AAF9C5BAAF72DE1D708EF9CC0F05418D\/2f0fba3e1e4c423d99f1a73291b3f4ac\/EPIC%20OF%20GILGAMESH%20%28summary%29.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;EPIC OF GILGAMESH (summary).pdf&quot;}\">EPIC OF GILGAMESH (summary).pdf<\/a><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_57f8965d-e254-4a51-9b25-dcff5045c5a5\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Additional Input<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_3cca6eaf-db7f-4c96-8676-bf636b276436\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20220730124810.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837748_1\"><\/a>",
