		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_233242fe-be4a-46f7-9ea8-33d92b44b425\"> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837778_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;200w.gif&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;200w.gif&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;200w.gif&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:531525,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/59\/590231C3992502FCE6F70892615D6B83\/990161aa22d84d959c2f4b0040c6eb99\/200w.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;200w.gif&quot;}\">200w.gif<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n <br> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_9645be31-c1a2-40cb-b7c7-3cbc9af6064a\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Overview<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #121416\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Through a lens of half-autobiography and half-cultural criticism, Miguel Syjuco‚Äôs award-winning novel makes a genuine attempt to appreciate the diversity and eccentricities of modern Manila and the fabric of the contemporary Philippines. The story itself‚Äîwith its light shading of New York noir and American thriller‚Äîtells the story of a young writer‚Äôs apprentice tasked with the self-appointed mission of writing an account of his deceased master‚Äôs life. The action that follows takes readers on a journey of meta-criticism, which does well to entertain while asking some serious questions about the state of Filipino literature as a whole.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_34c0d241-a694-4d19-9031-fcb759af5d07\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson Proper<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_c15d2f4c-e477-4996-ad34-f8c93c2a219e\"> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837779_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Syjuco.jpg&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;Syjuco.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;Syjuco.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:178943,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/59\/590231C3992502FCE6F70892615D6B83\/85afbb3d3e1740b5899ab91548f39fa6\/Syjuco.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Syjuco.jpg&quot;}\">Syjuco.jpg<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n <br> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_d36a388a-b73f-46eb-b7b1-de3b3bf0d349\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20220731063951.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837781_1\"><\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_fe6134e0-83aa-4ef3-ae9a-300cd16c1ef9\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">You may download the copy of the summary and enjoy reading!<\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837782_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 1).pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 1).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 1).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:264068,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/59\/590231C3992502FCE6F70892615D6B83\/bb3371654d184ea9891f1069ccd05585\/ILUSTRADO%20%28version%201%29.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 1).pdf&quot;}\">ILUSTRADO (version 1).pdf<\/a><\/p> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837783_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 2).pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 2).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 2).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:116054,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/59\/590231C3992502FCE6F70892615D6B83\/4bc5d6d658e14041891f9cbaae2ef65a\/ILUSTRADO%20%28version%202%29.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;ILUSTRADO (version 2).pdf&quot;}\">ILUSTRADO (version 2).pdf<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n<\/div>",
