		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_12feed5b-d6c8-402f-8539-1f0cd1b02895\"> \n <br> \n <p><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837786_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;7aUo.gif&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;7aUo.gif&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;7aUo.gif&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:524045,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/gif&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/59\/590231C3992502FCE6F70892615D6B83\/31898ff12c1446c79e86569f96d677bd\/7aUo.gif&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;7aUo.gif&quot;}\">7aUo.gif<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n<\/div> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_ec2bc3bd-25d6-4f61-b35e-668abe16768b\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>Overview<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #202124\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Life, although dictated by destiny, may yet remain malleable to the forces of individual determination. Self-determination is also the moving force by which a seemingly tragic turn of events unwittingly sets the stage for other, broader horizons.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">The text that you will read and learn about in this module is ‚ÄúMemoirs of a Geisha‚Äù (by Arthur Golden, 1997), a literary masterpiece about Japan.<\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">A memoir is like a diary, only, it accounts the most significant events about one‚Äôs own life. <\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>Lesson Proper<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>The Author<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837787_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;10856au.jpg&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;10856au.jpg&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;10856au.jpg&quot;,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/jpeg&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/89\/8917BFA34C5A27D5FF8A1BDE1769396B\/de85e3c110514e9d83d8da50c776eeb3\/10856au.jpg&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;10856au.jpg&quot;}\">10856au.jpg<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><em>penguin.com.au<\/em><\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;Although <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Arthur Golden <\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">is an American, his masterpiece ‚ÄúMemoirs of a Geisha‚Äù still qualifies as a Japanese masterpiece since the subject of the memoir is a Japanese and the Japanese culture about geishas, particularly about the geisha capital, Kyoto. Below are the accounts (encyclopedia.com, n.d.) about the genius behind the world-famous memoir: <\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>GOLDEN, Arthur<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"> 1956 - present&nbsp;PERSONAL: Born 1956, in Chattanooga, TN; married Trudy Legge, 1982; children: two. Education: Harvard College, B.A. (art history); Columbia University, M.A. (Japanese history), 1980; Boston University, M.A. (English), 1988. Hobbies and other interests: Classical guitar.&nbsp;ADDRESSES: Home‚ÄîP.O. Box 419, Brookline, MA 02446.&nbsp;CAREER: Writer. Worked for an English-language magazine in Tokyo,&nbsp;1980-82.<\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Before reading the memoir, watch the trailer of the movie. <\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/4L-xlmakQvc\" data-bbtype=\"video\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Memoirs of a Geisha (2005) Official Trailer 1 - Ziyi Zhang Movie&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/4L-xlmakQvc&quot;}\">Memoirs of a Geisha (2005) Official Trailer 1 - Ziyi Zhang Movie<\/a><\/p> \n <br> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>The Masterpiece<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p> \n <br> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"><strong>Professor‚Äôs Note <\/strong><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">on ‚ÄúMemoirs of a Geisha‚Äù<\/span><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_b9062d43-41e6-4f25-8247-eeae72a3fa72\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20220731090532.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837789_1\"><\/a> \n<div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_42759849-4ec4-4fe1-937d-e7f1e31f2208\"> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-17837790_1\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;W3 Memoirs of a Geisha by Arthur Golden (Japan).pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;W3 Memoirs of a Geisha by Arthur Golden (Japan).pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;W3 Memoirs of a Geisha by Arthur Golden (Japan).pdf&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application\/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@sessions\/89\/8917BFA34C5A27D5FF8A1BDE1769396B\/8b5d159c8fa24c9ea2f32d225be22a38\/W3%20Memoirs%20of%20a%20Geisha%20by%20Arthur%20Golden%20%28Japan%29.pdf&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;W3 Memoirs of a Geisha by Arthur Golden (Japan).pdf&quot;}\">W3 Memoirs of a Geisha by Arthur Golden (Japan).pdf<\/a><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">The memoir is four hundred plus pages.&nbsp;That is why I am sharing with you the film version (2005) of the masterpiece. If you choose the latter, here‚Äôs the link: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/malayancollegesmindanaoo365-my.sharepoint.com\/:v:\/g\/personal\/cbgravador_mcm_edu_ph\/EdoRA8y-1Z1GmMU1ly6YjakB_1Jiemo5pIOFbpgEf27LaQ?e=u2g2WA\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Memoirs of a Geisha<\/span><\/a><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br><\/p> \n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Enjoy reading\/watching, class!<\/span><\/p> \n<\/div>",
