		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This is to announce the schedule for the&nbsp;<strong>Face-to-face Module 2 Summative Assessment<\/strong>&nbsp;for the CHM031 Lecture Course. Please be reminded of the following details about the Summative Assessment:<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.cslocation@X@Screenshot%202023-10-02%20171759.png\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171759.png&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171759.png&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171759.png&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:13278,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/malayanmindanao.blackboard.com\/sessions\/04\/049CB38140088FBA66FEF9E43738EF66\/b8ea44efb10c4564a029512830560c48\/Screenshot%202023-10-02%20171759.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171759.png&quot;}\">Screenshot 2023-10-02 171759.png<\/a><\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Please read the reminders\/instructions to be implemented in administering the Summative Assessment.&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red\">NFI will be deducted points<\/span>.<\/p><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Answer Sheet Instructions:<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.cslocation@X@Screenshot%202023-10-02%20171817.png\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171817.png&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171817.png&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171817.png&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:59051,&quot;isDecorative&quot;:true,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;image\/png&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;inlineOnly&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/malayanmindanao.blackboard.com\/sessions\/04\/049CB38140088FBA66FEF9E43738EF66\/261e0ef7b1b74fc7aebf061a7d0b5503\/Screenshot%202023-10-02%20171817.png&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Screenshot 2023-10-02 171817.png&quot;}\">Screenshot 2023-10-02 171817.png<\/a><\/p><br><br><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">General Reminders:<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p>1.\tThe Summative exam is good for 1.5 hours. Make sure to arrive at the examination rooms on time.&nbsp;<\/p><p>2.\tUse a black or blue ink pen for your answers. No pencils for final answers.<\/p><p>3.\tOnly your pens, calculator, and small examination booklet are allowed on your tables. Bringing mobile phones or smart watches is not allowed.<\/p><p>4.\tMake sure to turn off or set your mobile phones to silent mode. Ringing phones during the examination might disturb other students taking the exam.<\/p><p>5.\tStrictly NO BORROWING of calculators.<\/p><p>6.\tThe back part of the calculator will be removed before getting in your assigned seats.&nbsp;<\/p><p>7.\tAnswer sheets will be provided. Shade the circles of your final answers completely.&nbsp;<\/p><p>8.\tNO ERASURES, double answers, or stray marks per item on the answer sheet. Otherwise, it will be marked wrong.<\/p><p>9.\tUse your examination booklet to show all solutions for questions that need computations\/drawings. Indicate the item number before each solution. BOX your final answers.<\/p><p>10.\tDon‚Äôt forget to write your exam details on the cover page of the exam booklet.<\/p><p>11.\tRipping or tearing of booklet pages is not allowed.<\/p><p>12.\tOnce the exam has started, no one can go out for breaks (e.g., bathroom breaks), borrow other materials, or take things out of their bags.<\/p><p>13.\tAny form of cheating or violation of academic integrity policy will merit consequences.<\/p><p>14.\tWhen finished, insert your questionnaire inside your examination booklet then sign the attendance form upon giving your papers.<\/p><br><p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">STUDY REMINDERS<\/span><\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Practice tests and formative assessments have been provided to help you prepare for the exam.<\/li><li>Utilize the guided solutions as needed to further understand the answers to formative assessments.<\/li><li>Read the chapters assigned for further knowledge.<\/li><li>Good luck and I'm rooting for you to pass this module!<\/li><\/ul>",
