		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Hi, A181 CHM031 Students!&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p>Welcome to&nbsp;<strong>CHM031: Chemistry for Engineers.<\/strong><\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I am Lorraine Jane Sanchez and I will be handling your section for this lecture course. I have started posting the course materials for this week.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We will not meet tomorrow yet. Please use our scheduled time tomorrow to familiarize yourself with our course.<\/p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kindly navigate starting from the&nbsp;<strong>Course Information<\/strong>&nbsp;module until&nbsp;<strong>Module 0,&nbsp;<\/strong>to give you the details and policies of this course. You may start answering the&nbsp;FA1.1 activity.&nbsp;<\/p>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We will have our<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">F2F orientation<\/span><\/strong>&nbsp;on our&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #046ef6\">Wednesday<\/span><span style=\"color: #046ef6\"><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span>schedule,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #046ef6\">August 09, 10:45 AM in Room 411<\/span>. Kindly accept the&nbsp;calendar invite through our MS Teams group so you won't miss the schedule.<\/p>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you were not automatically added to the group, you may join through this link:<\/p>\n <h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/teams.microsoft.com\/l\/team\/19%3a3Wu7PMHbQOQgJh9qG-6Q_2KM_eP5H48DEZWTGSAdAAA1%40thread.tacv2\/conversations?groupId=d5e96f27-5dfb-4eb8-bf80-7d1d644d8c01&amp;tenantId=9ddf6758-b8c5-4ce5-8bbf-f8c8cc9dd41d\">Chemistry for Engineers (A181)<\/a><\/h5>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">See you all on Wednesday!<\/p>\n <br>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Ma'am Lorraine<\/p>\n<\/div>",
