		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_2ec7e190-b310-45cf-9cf7-4a8dc76e63d9\"> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">In this module, we will discuss the <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><em>core of being a Malayan<\/em><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">. Module 1 and Module 2 are good for <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>eleven weeks<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">. Please be guided of the lessons to be covered so that we will be able to <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>accomplish all the needed tasks on time<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"> for this module.<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 1: MCM Vision, Mission, and Core Values<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 2: LC-OBE<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 3: MCM's Learning Management System, Digital Tools used in learning<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 4: Malayan Hymn<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Assessments<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">A. 1 Short Quiz after each lesson<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-Lessons 1, 2, and 4: Objective Type (true or false, matching type, multiple choice)<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-Lesson 3: Application (submission of PowerPoints Presentation)<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">B. Module 1 Final Assessment: Singing of the Malayan Hymn <\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Release Conditions<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-In order for you to access Lesson 2, Lesson 3, Lesson 4, Module 1 Learning Materials and Module 1 Final Assessment, you need to be able to get <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>6 points or higher in the short quizzes set<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">. <\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Please do not immediately answer the quizzes <\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">as you only have <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>2 attempts<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">. <\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-Lecture videos are in place to aid your learning. <\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">-You need to get <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>at least 6 points in the quizzes<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"> in order to access the lessons. For your guidance:<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Lesson 2: LC-OBE <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">- gain 6 points or higher for <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 1 Quiz<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Lesson 3: MCM Learning Management System and Digital Tools<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"> - gain 6 points or higher for <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 2 Quiz<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Lesson 4: The Malayan Hymn<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"> - gain 6 points or higher for <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 3 Quiz<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Module 1 Final Assessment<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"> - gain 6 points or higher for <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\"><strong>Lesson 4 Quiz<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n<\/div> \n<a data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_b88dc217-129e-4047-8861-68aa8f7f2491\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;UNSAFE_HTML_20210807134120.html&quot;}\" data-bbtype=\"embedded-unsafe-html\" href=\"@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav\/xid-18004855_1\"><\/a>",
