		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div data-bbid=\"bbml-editor-id_614178f3-8aa6-4d03-8df1-240afbb7b190\"> \n <br> \n <p><a href=\"https:\/\/assets.change.org\/photos\/5\/uj\/gm\/KFUJGMyTLOFDduT-1600x900-noPad.jpg?1586582580\" data-bbtype=\"image\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">https:\/\/assets.change.org\/photos\/5\/uj\/gm\/KFUJGMyTLOFDduT-1600x900-noPad.jpg?1586582580<\/a><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">In the previous module, you were exposed to the MCM as an educational institution - complete with the vision, mission, hymn, and traditions true to the academe. In this module, all of the underpinnings of MCM as an institution will be contextualized in real life. This module will teach you how to reinvent yourself, attain excellence, and cope with stress.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Module Outline<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The following are the lesson break down for this module:<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 5: Learning How to Learn<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 6: Advancing Man's Welfare<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 7: How to be Excellent&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 8: Coping with Stress&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Assessments<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The following will be the graded activities for this module:<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 5 - Multiple Choice and True or False (10 items)&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 6 - True or False (5 items)&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 7 - Multiple Choice and True or False (5 items)<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 8 - True or False (10 items)&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Module 2 Final Assessment - A Video Diary (Dear Future Me)&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Release Conditions&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">A. Akin to that of the first module, your lessons will be released according to your performance. <\/span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>You will need to answer the quizzes. <\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The release performance will start on lesson 6.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <ul> \n  <li><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 6 would have the lesson 5 quiz to be a trigger to release the content.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 7 would have the lesson 6 quiz to be a trigger to release the content.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Lesson 8 would have the lesson 7 quiz to be a trigger to release the content.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Module 2 Final Assessment would have the lesson 8 quiz to be a trigger to release the content.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li> \n <\/ul> \n <br> \n <p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">B. For each lesson quiz, you will be given only <\/span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>two attempts<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n<\/div>",
