		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Good day, students!<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">This is to inform those who got a C grade that you may now start your completion in this course. Please be guided with the dates and the process below:<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"background-color: #bfedd2; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong>Important Dates<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <ol> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">C graders have until <span style=\"background-color: #f8ff00;\"><strong>June 7, 2021<\/strong><\/span>&nbsp;to apply for&nbsp;<strong>RCC at the Registrar's Office<\/strong><\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">C graders will be allowed to submit assessment tasks\/projects\/take removal exams until <span style=\"background-color: #f8ff00;\"><strong>June 9, 2021<\/strong><\/span>.<\/span><\/li> \n <\/ol> \n <p><span style=\"background-color: #bfedd2; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong>Process<\/strong><\/span><\/p> \n <ol style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Calibri, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff; list-style-type: lower-alpha;\"> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The student requests for RCC from the Registrar. Visit this link&nbsp;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/MCMStudentCompletion\">https:\/\/bit.ly\/MCMStudentCompletion<\/a><\/span> \n   <div> \n    <table> \n     <tbody> \n      <tr> \n       <td> \n        <div> \n         <span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/MCMStudentCompletion\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.forms.office.net\/forms\/images\/urlpreview\/preview_logo_new.png\"><\/a><\/span> \n        <\/div> <\/td> \n       <td> \n        <div> \n         <span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/MCMStudentCompletion\">Fill | Student Request for Completion of Grade<\/a><\/span> \n        <\/div> \n        <div> \n         <span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Use this form to complete your \"C\" grade on courses taken 1st Semester SY2020-2021. Period covered for this request: College - 1st Sem Fill-out one form for every subject you will completing. Steps : 1. Fill-up the form with the details requested. Click submit. 2. You will receive thru email the \"Request for Course Completion form (RCC)\" Email back the RCC with your signature. You are given one week to complete the grade. 3. Pay P50.00\/course to the Treasury Office and send proof of transaction to treasury@mcm.edu and registrar@mcm.edu.ph 4. The Registrar will inform your professor of your request. 5. You will receive an email from your professor regarding the requirements and the deadline for completing the course\/subject. 6. After completing the requirements, your professor will process your grade completion with the Registrar. 7. You will receive an email notifying the posting of your new grade for the course. Deadline for the application to complete \"C\" grades will be on April 10, 2021<\/span> \n        <\/div> \n        <div> \n         <span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">bit.ly<\/span> \n        <\/div> <\/td> \n      <\/tr> \n     <\/tbody> \n    <\/table> \n   <\/div> <span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"> or email the Registrar.<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The Registrar sends the RCC to the student and the faculty.<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"background-color: #f8ff00; font-size: 0.875rem;\">The student needs to sign the RCC, to pay 50 Php (per RCC), and to send the RCC to the faculty.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The student<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000;\">c<\/span>ompletes the assigned tasks and informs the instructor.<\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #f8ff00;\">NO RCC NO GRADE Policy&nbsp;applies.<\/span>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000;\">c<\/span>ourse modules will be made available starting<strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: #f8ff00;\">May 3, 2021<\/span>.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #f8ff00;\">June 9, 2021 would be the last for 2Sem<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; background-color: #f8ff00;\">C<\/span>grade<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; background-color: #f8ff00;\">C<\/span>ompletion.<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/li> \n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">After June 9, 2021, all 2Sem<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000;\">C<\/span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000;\">Grades<\/span>will be automatically<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000;\">c<\/span>onverted to 5.0.<\/span><\/li> \n <\/ol> \n  \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Should there be other<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-style: #000000; font-weight: #000000; font-stretch: #000000; line-height: #000000; font-family: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000;\">c<\/span>oncerns, you may email me on Outlook or on Teams or inquire from the Registrar. Thank you and stay safe.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>",
