		"ITEM_NAME" : "CONCERN ABOUT ONLINE MEETING\/CONSULTATION ON TEAMS",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p>Hi, everyone!&nbsp;<\/p> \n <p>Please note that the online meeting on Teams is a refreshment only of our lessons in the modules. Still, all are not required to attend since the sessions will be recorded and posted in 'Consultation Recordings' on the sidebar. Also, you may visit our group on Teams to check the recordings and the conversions since all are already added [please make sure to use your MCM account to log-in].<\/p> \n <p>If you are worried about being left behind, please do not worry since the modules are self-paced, the assessments have no deadlines, and the online meetings are recorded. In that sense, you can access them at your convenience within the semester. Just make sure to manage your time to avoid piling up of works.<\/p> \n <p>Also, if you have further questions, you can always message me on Outlook or on Teams through this email, cjgjarabe@mcm.edu.ph every Weekdays from 8:00 am- 5:00 pm.<\/p> \n <p>Thank you and stay safe.<\/p>\n<\/div>",
