		"ITEM_NAME" : "Daniekou Arnoco",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>The maxim is basically understandable, the way it delivered tells us the meaning. It states that when creating and building something, the process it takes will be longer and time consuming but when you destroy something it will take a second to destroy what you've done. I realized whenever you build something we are very specific and we take our time but whenever we destroy something we are very free and the whole process will take a butterfly effect.<\/p>",
