		"COURSE_ID" : 3512986,
		"COURSE_NAME" : "Logic and Critical Thinking",
		"ITEM_ID" : 362318791,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "EXplaination",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>working on something new would take up alot of time and work for a person to perfect it. For an example, an actor may have perfected his or her art of acting for many years to be seen in big movies and to have a good reputation, but if someone find dirt on him\/her and posted it only to slander or may procure a beliveable story even if its not true, it will affect the reputation and the marketability of the actor, a specific example of this would be the case of Johny Depp and Amber herd, Amber told the media that Johny was a abusibve partner and the mainstream media jumped on the story to gain publicity, Johny's career went downhill, he lost big roles and suffered mentaly and resorted to vices, but recently it was proven the accusations were false and it was Amber who was abusive to Johny.<\/p>",
