		"ITEM_ID" : 362318878,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "Greatness",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0.0in 0.0in 8.0pt;line-height: 107.0%;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Massive skyscrapers and historical landmarks are a testament to greatness. The grandeur of these buildings was made possible by humanity. However, in modern society, &nbsp;such marvel is no longer confined in the size of a structure but within humans themselves. As humanity progressed, the measurement of greatness came in many forms, one of which is intangible.<\/p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0.0in 0.0in 8.0pt;line-height: 107.0%;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In a world where the credibility of information is hard to discern, there is nothing more valuable today than trust. Trust plays a huge factor on a person‚Äôs life, be it choosing a reliable news source, conducting business transactions or even being someone‚Äôs friend.&nbsp;<\/p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0.0in 0.0in 8.0pt;line-height: 107.0%;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Additionally, another thing that becomes easier to gain is reputation. With the help of technology, people can reach out to more individuals&nbsp; especially when one is advocating a certain agenda. Furthermore, an individual‚Äôs prominence is essential because it allows one to gain the respect and trust of people. Social media helps increase the size of their platform and stature as well.<\/p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0.0in 0.0in 8.0pt;line-height: 107.0%;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Truly, trust and reputation are highly sought after and become increasingly difficult to attain overtime. But much like dominoes, something as infinitesimally small as a puff of air can destroy countless hours‚Äô worth of work. Greatness should not be measured by years alone, but rather how long it withstood the test of time.<\/p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0.0in 0.0in 8.0pt;line-height: 107.0%;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri , sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<\/p>",
