		"COURSE_NAME" : "Logic and Critical Thinking",
		"ITEM_ID" : 362318877,
		"ITEM_NAME" : "Logic and Critical Thinking",
		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<p>for me its like trust. It takes years for us to build but only a fraction of a second for it to break and takes forever for it to repair. don't destroy other peoples hard work because it might've taken them so much time to build. be humble and respect everyone for what they do. everybody has different ambitions in life.<\/p>",
