		"ITEM_DESCRIPTION" : "<!-- {\"bbMLEditorVersion\":1} --><div>\n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Good day, students!&nbsp;<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">This is to inform you that the MCM grade (e.g 1.0, 1.25...) has been reflected already as your final grade in this course. Also, to those who got a C grade, you will comply with your missed assessments during the summer, and failure to comply will automatically convert your grade into 5.0.<\/span><\/p> \n <p><span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem;\">Should you have concerns and clarifications, feel free to email me on outlook or on teams during working hours. Thank you and stay safe.<\/span><\/p> \n  \n \n<\/div>",
